                        <p>
                            ● at an Elexnet pay terminal (cash only);
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            ● via your account on the local pay parking website:
                            <a href="https://my.rndparking.ru/">https://my.rndparking.ru/</a>;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            ● using the Rostov-on-Don Parking mobile app for iOS and Android;
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            ● with a text message to 2888.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            When you have parked your car, you have 15 minutes to pay for your parking. The fine for
                            unpaid parking
                            ranges up to 3000 roubles. If your car was towed in a pay-park area, contact the call centre
                            at +7 (863)
                            285-1001.
                        </p>
                        <a href="https://rndparking.ru/">Pay-parking in Rostov-on-Don</a>
                        </p>
                    {% endblock %}
                {% endembed %}
